        public void updateObserverList()
        Update observers to contain everybody who is in the same world within data.chunkActivationRange and nobdoy who is not in the same world or not within data.chunkViewDistance, measured in chunk distance.

      • addObserver

        public void addObserver(org.bukkit.entity.Player player)
